content.p: Nottingham School of Economics (NSE) is one of the top economics departments globally; the prestigious Tilburg ranking of the top 100 economics schools places NSE 38 in the world. The University of Nottingham is ranked in the top 100 universities in the world and is internationally renowned for high-impact research and teaching excellence.
